              - kind: EndOfLineComment
                text: "' To get the same return from Quat2Euler, the following Euler angle constraints should be observed:"
              - kind: Newline
                text: "\r\n"
              - kind: Whitespace
                text: "    "
              - kind: EndOfLineComment
                text: "'       pi   >  euler.x  >  -pi            ' In theory, 180 (or -180) should be possible, but not here."
